data.name: Bike Racing
data.rules:
Complete the Course by completing the objective of running over all of the King Chims.

Since All King Chims are required, the Bike Glitch is not allowed under this rule set.

This category is IGT and uses the Race Timer present on the screen at the end of the race for its final time.

Only submit IGT

data.name: Rebirth
data.rules:
Timing Start
For Normal Game: After Selecting "Normal Game"
For Cheat Mode: After the Confirmation Screen for the Cheat Mode changes.

Timing End
When the Data Drain bullet lands on Azure Flame God.

data.name: Vol.3 All Fights
data.rules:
Must use a Vol.3 Redemption Save.
No other restrictions on savefile used.

You must complete all 16 avatar fights once.
Fights may be done in any order of the runner's choosing.

Timing Start
After removing all tutorial pop-ups from the fights, timing starts upon selecting the first fight.

Timing End
When the final data drain bullet lands in the 16th Avatar Fight.

data.name: Any%
data.rules:
- Finish the game starting from a new save file. 
- RTA (Timer starts upon pressing New Game, and ends upon defeating the Final Boss)

data.name: Any% NG+
data.rules:
- Finish the game starting from a New Game+ file. All items/equipment carried over are allowed.
- RTA (Timer starts upon accepting NG+ file, and ends upon defeating the Final Boss)

data.name: Any%
data.rules:
Timing starts from New Game
Timing Ends when the final boss is defeated.

data.name: Any%
data.rules:
Goal: Defeat Skeith - Timing starts from  New Game and ends after the final blow is landed on Skeith.  
In-game time is acquired from the Data Clear Flag - save after credits.

data.name: Any%
data.rules: Start from New Game and end time at the last hit on Magus. In game time is gotten from saving the data flag after the credits.
